---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Kids Candle Making Class"
  description="Safe and fun candle-making classes for children in Centerville, TN. Age-appropriate creative experiences your kids will love!"
  price="$15-22 per child"
  duration="1.5 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="kids candle making, children's art classes, safe candle making, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Kids Candle Making Class - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>
      Introduce your children to the joy of candle making in our safe, fun, age-appropriate Kids Candle Making Classes. We've designed our process specifically for children's safety and enjoyment, making it a memorable creative experience.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      Kids will pour beautiful soy candles with help from our experienced staff. They'll choose their own fragrances and colors, creating unique candles they're proud to take home. We use special safety measures to ensure kids stay safe while having maximum fun!
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pre-measured wax (safe for kids)</li>
      <li>Kid-friendly fragrance options</li>
      <li>Beautiful containers to choose from</li>
      <li>Color customization options</li>
      <li>Adult supervision throughout</li>
      <li>Take-home finished candles</li>
      <li>Safety instruction and best practices</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Age Groups</h3>
    <p>Classes designed for ages 6-12, with activities adjusted for different age groups. Younger kids receive more hands-on help, while older kids get more independence in the pouring process.</p>

    <h3>Safety First</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Pre-warmed, measured wax (no hot handling)</li>
      <li>Temperature-controlled environment</li>
      <li>Adult supervision ratio 1:4 kids</li>
      <li>Safe, age-appropriate techniques</li>
      <li>Clear safety instructions before starting</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and safety briefing (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Fragrance and color selection (5 minutes)</li>
      <li>Guided candle pouring (45 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches (10 minutes)</li>
      <li>Take-home their beautiful candle!</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Single class: $15-22 per child</li>
      <li>Monthly passes available</li>
      <li>Group rates for schools and organizations</li>
    </ul>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Enroll your young candle maker!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"My son was so proud making his own candle! He's used it and already wants to come back for the next class!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Mom - Nicole</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The staff was amazing with the kids. Safe, fun, and my daughter created something beautiful she's super proud of!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Aunt Linda</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Best way to get kids creative and off screens! Both my kids want to make candles again!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Dad - Tom</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Kids Pottery Painting Class</h3>
        <p>Fun, age-appropriate pottery painting classes designed for children.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/kids-pottery-painting-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Family Pottery Painting Experience</h3>
        <p>Multi-generational creative fun with pottery painting for the whole family.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/family-pottery-painting-experience" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Paint and Pour Pottery Candle</h3>
        <p>Combine pottery painting with candle making for double the creativity.</p>
        <a href="/art-studio/paint-and-pour-pottery-candle" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
